Puppet module: ec2

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages ec2
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include ec2              # Install and run ec2 with standard configurations.
include ec2::disable     # Disable ec2 service.
include ec2::disableboot # Disable ec2 service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include ec2::absent      # Remove ec2 package.

DEPENDENCIES:
common::untar-gz 
